org.apache.spark.scheduler

Class ApplicationEventListener

  • Object
    • org.apache.spark.scheduler.ApplicationEventListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SparkListener

    public class ApplicationEventListener
extends Object
implements SparkListener
    A simple listener for application events.

    This listener expects to hear events from a single application only. If events from multiple applications are seen, the behavior is unspecified.
